7094507583", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "融災350 全血肉 不求人 推廣血肉", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1243105047332524043", "1174179734373019748"]}
{"id": "1243841887924912218", "channel_id": "1243841887924912218", "type": 0, "author_id": "1139928180254326927", "author_name": "rock1234_47882", "author_bot": false, "content": "属于是打的比较痛苦的一次融灾，难度集中在3，4关\n第1，5关不同以往，显得尤其简单（我红是女王！）\n卡茜亚建议使用能对群的角色攻略（油污，阿红之类）以及能够无视敌方前排的宁妃", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T08:23:35.546000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1243841888302272532", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-39-57_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160115, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841888302272532/Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-39-57_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa87&is=69f9a907&hm=dc8b15c89741f2dd48368735733c741e84ac31eb37106d2e277b0ae028fce79f&"}, {"id": "1243841888667172874", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-34-86_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 160727, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841888667172874/Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-34-86_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa87&is=69f9a907&hm=3203f62e0298aff7dc80b10ae8c8027b8f21b5c3cf4c4cd05b60cbbc4b48c516&"}, {"id": "1243841889002852362", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-06-29_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 253334, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841889002852362/Screenshot_2024-05-25-16-10-06-29_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa87&is=69f9a907&hm=2b531df6675ba64a025e2cf098e8a25b081df9e3dce018d8d36b3e41d55e77e6&"}, {"id": "1243841889376014356", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-15-35-54-00_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 218786, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841889376014356/Screenshot_2024-05-25-15-35-54-00_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa87&is=69f9a907&hm=9f8398cca0d91ee736b40cb21930eee192f6d88572fcc91467b5444c4d479922&"}, {"id": "1243841889715884042", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-13-37-46-80_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 228115, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841889715884042/Screenshot_2024-05-25-13-37-46-80_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa87&is=69f9a907&hm=12769dc180064f35ab038a828dcd0fbe514084d8c78b37d899846b4c5035af9a&"}, {"id": "1243841890034384956", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-09-53-02-65_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157577, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841890034384956/Screenshot_2024-05-25-09-53-02-65_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa88&is=69f9a908&hm=cf329a6044f6fea43639adbc131a9580dedf01235b4f2a722c58aa863f205d17&"}, {"id": "1243841890390904873", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-09-38-58-43_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 286363, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243841887924912218/1243841890390904873/Screenshot_2024-05-25-09-38-58-43_1c2ea364798f98bd84a81a8c53b45cfb.jpg?ex=69fafa88&is=69f9a908&hm=6ebbf31de7c646f292c30fab853b9a8de3cf12ea371a228b9c75522f6adab39b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1243841887924912218", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "第九期融灾通关！", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181143392739147778"]}
{"id": "1243793709368344586", "channel_id": "1243793709368344586", "type": 0, "author_id": "1073914607741177866", "author_name": "scholar_2", "author_bot": false, "content": "五套卡組分別是\n水母🦈；希洛莉莉；血肉環拉；紅花泰；混沌24\n\n1-3:隱秘人稱大我們的家。boss也沒什麼攻擊性，懲戒的死抗都沒用上，到第七回合秒了\n\n2-3:羽翼，非常適合打擊隊的造物，算力上限和大量打擊提供。需要注意6回合小怪會封印，儘可能先殺掉以免妨礙第七回合輸出\n\n3-3:中規中矩的造物，加速陣容運轉，這裡我采用環拉泰旖絲雙轉體系（具體見另一篇帖子https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1241414224551346336）圖裡的陣容建議女仆替換掉奧吉爾，生存更強且可以有效降低算力壓力（筆者打的時候卡手卡爛了）\n簡化版-開局跨越拿超越，超越拿古老，第二回合環拉大→艾瑞卡銀鈅給環拉→泰旖絲複製古老→三張古老→曡環拉buff→特效超越拿古老回手\n可達成無限大招（非容災環境），容災環境也可雙轉3-5回合（視造物和boss壓力而定），能提供大量的永久力量\n道中由於環拉覺醒不穩定上手，故轉完第一次即可複製命定清場即可\n打魔術師需要注意二階段的屏障小怪，要留好環拉大招拉命定回手打連著2回合的三命定爆發，或者環拉變純白直接找牌庫的銀鈅也可\n\n4-3:入迷，多段的神。紅泰艾菲秒了，沒什麼好說的，水母練度高的也可以使用水母\n\n5-3:這裡先解釋一下給的分別是什麼\n第一個是55永久力量+50毒和99臨時力量\n第二個是拿4個人的1張0費打擊+群體5狂氣和拿1個人的3張0費打擊+單體10狂氣\n第三個是回復30%最大生命值的血量+獲得易傷和獲得30%最大生命值的護盾\n以上均為二選一，保留、消耗。\n個人用的混沌24，思路沒什麼好講解的（\n說一下boss機制，注意在boss出手多段的時候要用夫人送的卡把小怪拉前排先殺，這樣可以取消boss的臨時力量。還有一種特攻思路是水母戈利亞，boss機制給很多過牌和算力，瘋狂過給boss曡力量然後強者偷過來（後期boss能有大幾百的臨時力量，直接偷爽）\n\n以上。", "timestamp": "2024-05-25T05:12:08.883000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-05-25T05:22:32.663000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}, {"emoji": "🙏", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1243793709573603438", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-12-48-39-720_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 180250, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243793709368344586/1243793709573603438/Screenshot_2024-05-25-12-48-39-720_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg?ex=69fb7668&is=69fa24e8&hm=a79fd8bf326620bc785bab777f3e8d1b7d2107271efc621d1827947c7f25456f&"}, {"id": "1243793709846368346", "filename": "Screenshot_2024-05-25-12-48-36-042_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 175097, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1243793709368344586/1243793709846368346/Screenshot_2024-05-25-12-48-36-042_com.qookkagames.z1.gw.hk.j